
It's one script to import a DB from WordPress ( is checked in wp version 3.3.1).
First you need create one instance in opennemas.
This script check some categories and import articles,opinions, comments & images.
You need modify data in config-data.ini

HOW USE:

1. You need change config.ini
2. Execute ./wordpress-importer.php
3. Is generated refactor_ids table in database with old and new ids

NOTES:

First: If you need import categories, you have save in config var "categories".
You write originID = newId if the category exists, but if not exitst newID=0.
Then you write category data in config var "newCategories".

Second: If you want to import wp images, you need save images folder in local dir
and save this in config var [media] directory.

Third: As wordpress doesn't have author opinions you have config authorOpinionID.
If you want import opinion you have assign originID catogory the newID=4



ATENTION!
If you need to make 30 redirections for old urls:
     #http://www.url.com/category/politica
      #http://www.url.com/category/tendencias/medios-comunicacion
    RewriteRule ^category/([a-z0-9\-]+)/?$ /seccion/$1/ [R=301,L,NC]
    RewriteRule ^category/([a-z0-9\-]+)/([a-z0-9\-]+)/?$ /seccion/$2/ [R=301,L,NC]
      # opinion categories
    RewriteRule ^category/opinion/?$ /opinion/ [R=301,L,NC]
    RewriteRule ^category/opinion/colaboradores/?$ /opinion/ [R=301,L,NC]

      #tags
    #http://www.url.com/tag/consejo-nacional-de-transicion
    RewriteRule ^tag/([a-z0-9\-]+)/?$ /seccion/$1/ [R=301,L,NC]

      #Old Static pages
    RewriteRule ^contacto /estaticas/contacto.html [R=301,L,NC]
    RewriteRule ^publicidad /estaticas/publicidad.html [R=301,L,NC]
    RewriteRule ^feed/?$ /rss/listado [R=301,L,NC]

      #Inner Article - Opinion
    #http://www.url.com/3501-madrid-y-rabat-sellan-un-pacto-secreto-de-ayuda-mutua.html
    RewriteRule ^([0-9]+)\-([a-z0-9\-]+).html?$ /controllers/redirect-imported-elements.php?content_type=article&content_id=$1 [L,NC]

